    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new ride that\u2019s ready for all your upcoming adventures? I'm selling my trusty car, and it is in such great shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a dream, making it the perfect dependable choice for your daily commute or weekend getaways. It\u2019s super clean and has plenty of life left in it. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see how smoothly it handles. Drop me a message if you're interested\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
