    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2008 Porsche Cayman S, a mid-engine platform engineered for surgical precision. This example features the 3.4L flat-six M97.21 powerplant, utilizing VarioCam Plus for an optimized torque curve and 295 hp. The longitudinal 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile gate engagement, sending power through a robust drivetrain. The chassis is equipped with staggered 19-inch alloys and a suspension geometry that maintains neutral handling characteristics under high lateral G-loads. Braking is handled by four-piston aluminum monobloc fixed calipers over vented and cross-drilled rotors, ensuring minimal fade. The hydraulic steering rack remains communicative and leak-free. Recent preventative maintenance includes a drive belt replacement and a comprehensive borescope inspection to confirm cylinder wall integrity. This is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car for those who value analog feedback and engineering excellence.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
