      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and long-term care. The exterior finish remains vibrant and glossy, with only the minor, expected road wear consistent with careful use. The body panels are straight, and the alloy wheels are in great shape. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has been kept smoke-free; the upholstery is supple with no tears, and every button, dial, and digital display functions perfectly. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It has been serviced at regular intervals, featuring a responsive engine and a transmission that shifts seamlessly through every gear. Recent updates include a new set of tires and a fresh fluid service. It drives straight and true, offering a quiet, composed ride that feels solid on the highway and nimble in the city. This is a dependable, well-documented vehicle perfect for someone who values both aesthetics and mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
